welcome:
Thank you for your interest in this research study. 



The study should take you around 8 minutes to complete.



This survey will be best displayed on a laptop or desktop computer.

 

We are data science graduate students in the Masters of Information and Data Science program at the University of California, Berkeley. We are researching how people perceive political bias and factualness in the titles of articles from major publications when presented in a reddit news feed.  You will be presented titles in the format of a reddit news feed and asked to answer some questions about them. All of your responses will be kept completely confidential.  To be eligible for this study you must: 

 

	Be 18 years or older
	Live in the United States
	Be able to read and comprehend English fluently
	Possess a basic understanding of liberal vs. conservative viewpoints in the United States


 If you choose to participate,  you acknowledge that you meet the eligibility requirement. Your participation is voluntary, and you may choose to terminate your participation in the study at any time and for any reason.
